  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "eth-portfolio-3contract-buffer-sell-100y",
    "name": "ETH-Liq-LTV-TPP-COM-COL-BUF-SELL-1mon-30-100Y1Y-daily",
    "description": "ACTUS DeFi ETH Portfolio: OPTION B - BUFFER-FIRST LIQUIDATION DEFENSE\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\nOPTION B: SOPHISTICATED BUFFER-FIRST STRATEGY (vs Option A: Protocol Liquidation)\n  ✅ Sells from 4.0 ETH BUFFER (not collateral)\n  ✅ Preserves 3.0 ETH collateral quantity CONSTANT\n  ✅ LTV always calculated using original 3.0 ETH\n  ✅ Circuit breaker: max 3 interventions, min 1.0 ETH reserve\n  ✅ Falling knife detection: stops if price drops >20% in 48hr\n  ✅ 24-hour cooldown between interventions\n  ✅ DeFi correctness: matches keeper bot / DeFi Saver behavior\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n\nKEY DIFFERENCE FROM OPTION A:\n  Option A: Protocol liquidates collateral → LTV = loan / (depleting collateral)\n  Option B: User defends via buffer → LTV = loan / (CONSTANT 3.0 ETH)\n  \n  Example after $660 intervention:\n    Option A: LTV = $3,548 / (2.34 ETH × $2,200) = 68.9% ❌ Still stressed\n    Option B: LTV = $3,548 / (3.00 ETH × $2,200) = 53.8% ✅ Much healthier\n\nPORTFOLIO STRUCTURE:\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════\nTotal ETH: 7.0 ETH\n  - Collateral ETH: 3.0 ETH (pledged to loan, NEVER CHANGES)\n  - Buffer ETH: 4.0 ETH (defense fund, depletes on intervention)\n\nContracts:\n1. COM (ETH-Collateral-CompetingRisk-01): 3.0 ETH collateral\n2. COM (ETH-Buffer-Portfolio-01): 4.0 ETH buffer\n3. PAM (DeFi-ETH-CompetingRisk-01): $5,000 loan with behavioral models\n\nBEHAVIORAL MODELS:\n  1. TwoDimensionalPrepaymentModel — voluntary rate-driven deleveraging\n  2. BufferLTVModel — keeper bot LTV defense (NEW for Option B)\n\nCIRCUIT BREAKER PARAMETERS:\n  maxInterventions: 3\n  minBufferReserve: 1.0 ETH (never touch last 1.0 ETH)\n  maxBufferUsagePerIntervention: 33% (max 1.32 ETH per use)\n  cooldownMillis: 86400000 (24 hours)\n  fallingKnifePriceDropThreshold: 0.20 (20%)\n  fallingKnifeTimeWindowMillis: 172800000 (48 hours)\n\nScenario: ETH: $2,800 → $1,870 (-33%), Rate: 5.0% → 7.65%\nPeriod: 100-year perpetual, simulating first year\n\nOpen Postman Console (Ctrl+Alt+C) before running to see detailed intervention logs.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
